    <h2>Our Programs</h2>
            <h3>Youth Development</h3>
            <p>Empowering young people with leadership skills, confidence, and civic responsibility through mentorship, training, and community engagement initiatives.</p>
            <h3>Climate Action</h3>
            <p>Advocating for environmental sustainability, our Climate Action Program educates and mobilizes communities for eco-friendly practices and climate resilience.</p>
            <h3>Digital Inclusion</h3>
            <p>Bridging the digital divide in rural communities, we provide access to technology and digital literacy training, enabling full participation in the digital era.</p>
            <h3>Girls Leadership</h3>
            <p>Fostering the next generation of female leaders, our Girls Leadership Program provides mentorship, educational support, and empowerment opportunities.</p>
            <h3>Health and Well-being</h3>
            <p>Promoting healthy behaviors and sexual and reproductive health rights, ensuring communities have the knowledge and resources to lead healthier lives.</p>
